      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Monday it will be seen whether or\nnot the Northern Pacific railroad will\nBrowne street across the tracks of\nthe company. City Engineer McIn-\ntyre stated today that the stakes for\nthe grade would be set tomorrow\nafter which the street commissioners\ncould go ahead with the work.\n\n\n1t is stated that in all probability\nthe men will start in to open up the\nstreet Monday. 1t is expected the\nrailroad will take steps to enjoin the\ncity from completing the work."
